<view class='swiper'>
  <swiper class='swiper_container'
          indicator-dots='true'
          autoplay='true'
          interval='5000'>
    <block wx:for="{{images}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
      <swiper-item>
        <image src="{{item}}" class="slide-image"/>
      </swiper-item>
    </block>
  </swiper>
  <view class='post-container'>
    <view class='post-author-date'>
      <image src='/images/avatar/2.png' class='post-author'></image>
      <text class='post-date'>Sep 18 2016</text>
    </view>
    <text class='post-title'>正是虾肥蟹壮时</text>
    <image src='/images/posts/crab.png' class='post-image'></image>
    <text class='post-content'>菊黄蟹正肥，品尝秋之味。徐志摩把,“看初花的荻芦”和“到楼外楼吃蟹”,并列为秋天来杭州不能错过的风雅之事；用林妹妹的话讲是“螯封嫩玉双双满</text>
    <view class='post-like'>
      <image src='/images/icon/chat.png' class='post-like-image'></image>
      <text class='post-like-font'>96</text>
      <image src="/images/icon/view.png" class='post-like-image'></image>
      <text class='post-like-font'>112</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
